name: Simorgh Arrival
desc: Discard 1 Winged Beast monster; add 2 "Simorgh" monsters with different Attributes from your Deck to your hand. You can banish this card from your GY; reveal 1 Winged Beast monster from your hand, and if you do, for the rest of this turn, any monster with that revealed monster's name in your hand loses 1 Level. You can only active 1 "Simorgh Arrival" per turn.
